Demonstrate external offsets:

e_axis.ini         -- simple identity kins
e_axis_shutoff.ini -- shutoff for limit trespass

Usage:
  1) Estop OFF  (F1)
  2) Machine ON (F2)
  3) HOME All   (Ctrl-Home)
  4) Test external offset functionality using the
     sim_pin gui to alter the per-axis hal pins:
       axis.*.eoffset-enable
       axis.*.eoffset-scale
       axis.*.eoffset-counts
  5) For the e_axis_shutoff.ini example, automatic
     shutoff is controlled by the enable_shutoff
     signal (also provided with sim_pin) 

Notes:
  The ini file setting [AXIS_*]OFFSET_AV_RATIO=value
  controls external offsets velocity, acceleration

  Allowed values:
    0.0 <= OFFSET_AV_RATIO <= 0.9

  A value of 0 disables external offsets.

For more information, see documentation chapter for
External-offsets
